OL,3,CFamilies can't afford sports and PE
OL,4,Ckit, warns Sir Gareth Southgate
OL,6,FFormer England manager Sir Gareth
OL,7,FSouthgate has warned that families
OL,8,F"can't afford to buy kit" to take part
OL,9,Fin sport and PE lessons.
OL,11,FSir Gareth said there was a "risk kids
OL,12,Fend up in front of screens a lot of
OL,13,Fthe time" rather than being active and
OL,14,Foutside in a "difficult time where
OL,15,Feconomically a lot of families are
OL,16,Fstruggling".
