OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778115794
OL,3,CFamilies can't afford sports and PE
OL,4,Ckit, warns Sir Gareth Southgate
OL,6,FThe former England men's football
OL,7,Fmanager made the comments while
OL,8,Fpromoting The Multibank charity
OL,9,Fcampaign, which helps families across
OL,10,Fthe UK access essential items `
OL,11,Fincluding sports equipment.
OL,13,FIn an exclusive interview with the
OL,14,FPress Association, Sir Gareth said:
OL,15,F"We're talking about participation in
OL,16,FPE lessons, in being able to play
OL,17,Fsport.
OL,19,F"Unfortunately, some families are
OL,20,Freally challenged on that ` they can't
OL,21,Fafford to buy kit.
OL,26,@wD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
