OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778115794
OL,3,CFamilies can't afford sports and PE
OL,4,Ckit, warns Sir Gareth Southgate
OL,6,F"Very often people have to make a
OL,7,Freally horrible decision between
OL,8,Fessentials, groceries or spending on
OL,9,Fwhat for a lot of people aren't luxury
OL,10,Fitems, but can be in terms of football
OL,11,Fboots, trainers, sports kit."
OL,13,FSir Gareth, who was England manager
OL,14,Ffrom 2016 to 2024, added: "In a time
OL,15,Fwhen there's a risk kids end up in
OL,16,Ffront of screens a lot of the time `
OL,17,Fto be active and outside is really
OL,18,Fimportant.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@]O]vD@[OU
