OL,3,CFamilies can't afford sports and PE
OL,4,Ckit, warns Sir Gareth Southgate
OL,6,F"Every child deserves the right to
OL,7,Fplay sport. It's important for them
OL,8,Fphysically. There are so many other
OL,9,Faspects to playing sport that are
OL,10,Fhelpful."
OL,12,FSir Gareth said he was approached to
OL,13,Ftake part in the campaign by former
OL,14,Fprime minister Gordon Brown, who is
OL,15,Fpresident of The Multibank charity.
