OL,3,CFamilies can't afford sports and PE
OL,4,Ckit, warns Sir Gareth Southgate
OL,6,FAmazon is launching a new initiative
OL,7,Fwhere every third purchase of selected
OL,8,Fsports products will be matched with a
OL,9,Fdonation to The Multibank from May 7
OL,10,Fto June 4.
OL,12,FThe campaign comes as new YouGov data
OL,13,Frevealed around one in six parents
OL,14,F(15%) said their children have had to
OL,15,Fgive up their sporting ambitions as
OL,16,Fthey can't afford the kit or equipment
OL,17,Fto take part.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
