OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778115794
OL,3,CFamilies can't afford sports and PE
OL,4,Ckit, warns Sir Gareth Southgate
OL,6,FThe data, from a sample of 6451 adults
OL,7,Ftaken last month, revealed that around
OL,8,Fthree in four parents (72%) of
OL,9,Fchildren aged four-18 believe a lack
OL,10,Fof access to sports equipment leads to
OL,11,Ffewer opportunities for those from
OL,12,Flower-income families.
OL,14,FTwo in five parents (40%) with gross
OL,15,Fhousehold income under #30,000 cited
OL,16,Ffootball as the main activity they had
OL,17,Fto give up, the study found.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
